#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:123
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"|Option |\tDescription |\n"
"| ------| ----------- |\n"
"|`-g GID` |\tNew `GID` of the group to modify.\n"
