#. type: Fenced code block
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/06-users.md:856
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Shell > useradd -N test2\n"
"Shell > id test2\n"
"uid=1001(test2) gid=100(users) groups=100(users)\n"
